  "title": "Love on Sunny Island",
  "genre": "romance",
  "summary": "Emily meets a man on a sunny island and they talk.",
  "coverScene": "A young couple walking hand in hand along a secluded white sand beach with turquoise water and green palm trees in the background.",
  "levels": {
    "B2": {
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Emily arrived on the beautiful Sunny Island for a short summer holiday.",
              "audioStart": 0.1,
              "audioEnd": 3.612
            },
            {
              "text": "The sun was bright and the water was clear.",
              "audioStart": 4.475,
              "audioEnd": 6.675
            },
            {
              "text": "On her first day, she went to a local cafe where she met Jack.",
              "audioStart": 7.537,
              "audioEnd": 11.062
            },
            {
              "text": "Jack was a tall man who had also come to the island for a week.",
              "audioStart": 11.925,
              "audioEnd": 15.075
            },
            {
              "text": "They talked for a long time and felt a deep connection.",
              "audioStart": 15.938,
              "audioEnd": 18.788
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "The next morning, they decided to walk along the coast to find a quiet place.",
              "audioStart": 19.65,
              "audioEnd": 23.938
            },
            {
              "text": "They walked for hours and eventually lost their way.",
              "audioStart": 24.8,
              "audioEnd": 27.462
            },
            {
              "text": "While they were searching for a path, they found a hidden beach that was surrounded by large trees.",
              "audioStart": 28.325,
              "audioEnd": 33.038
            },
            {
              "text": "If they had not been lost, they would never have discovered this secret place.",
              "audioStart": 33.9,
              "audioEnd": 37.663
            },
            {
              "text": "The beach was silent and perfect.",
              "audioStart": 38.525,
              "audioEnd": 40.312
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "As the sun began to set, they realized they had to return to the hotel.",
              "audioStart": 41.175,
              "audioEnd": 45.138
            },
            {
              "text": "They started to walk back through a narrow forest path.",
              "audioStart": 46,
              "audioEnd": 48.763
            },
            {
              "text": "During the walk, they shared personal stories about their lives and dreams.",
              "audioStart": 49.625,
              "audioEnd": 53.425
            },
            {
              "text": "Emily felt that she could tell Jack anything.",
              "audioStart": 54.288,
              "audioEnd": 56.525
            },
            {
              "text": "He listened carefully as she spoke about her future plans.",
              "audioStart": 57.388,
              "audioEnd": 60.438
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "They finally reached the main road when the stars were already in the sky.",
              "audioStart": 61.3,
              "audioEnd": 64.9
            },
            {
              "text": "The night was warm and the air was soft.",
              "audioStart": 65.763,
              "audioEnd": 67.8
            },
            {
              "text": "They stopped for a moment, and Emily wondered if they would see each other again.",
              "audioStart": 68.662,
              "audioEnd": 72.388
            },
            {
              "text": "If the holiday ended tomorrow, would their friendship continue?",
              "audioStart": 73.25,
              "audioEnd": 76.338
            },
            {
              "text": "Jack smiled and promised that they would stay in contact.",
              "audioStart": 77.2,
              "audioEnd": 79.912
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "The last day of the holiday came too quickly.",
              "audioStart": 80.775,
              "audioEnd": 83.112
            },
            {
              "text": "They spent the morning at the cafe where they first met.",
              "audioStart": 83.975,
              "audioEnd": 86.713
            },
            {
              "text": "They exchanged phone numbers and promised to write to each other.",
              "audioStart": 87.575,
              "audioEnd": 90.537
            },
            {
              "text": "Although they were sad to leave, they were happy that they had met.",
              "audioStart": 91.4,
              "audioEnd": 94.463
            },
            {
              "text": "A new relationship had started on Sunny Island.",
              "audioStart": 95.325,
              "audioEnd": 97.838
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "audio": "audio/b2/st-0097.mp3",
